'''Nampat''' is the twenty-second track of  ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power (Season One: Amazon Original Series Soundtrack)]]''. This track occurs in [[Udûn (episode)|episode five]] as a war-chant which was used by the "children" of [[Adar (The Rings of Power)|Adar]] during their march to the [[Watchtower of Ostirith]] and then again during their march to [[Tirharad]].

